cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language explanations and their use in augmenting training data for text classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel framework for this task, which involves deep learning techniques, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with semantic parsing and logical forms, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper also mentions experiments and performance evaluation, which are related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
